main event: A witness observed a large, silver object and two smaller, blinking objects moving in a circular path and course.
interesting points: The witness took photographs of the sighted objects.
The report indicates that ATIC Form 164 was sent to the observer with a request to forward the negative or prints of the photographs.
The report mentions that the results of the analysis of the photographs, if any, will be forwarded to ATIC from the headquarters.
The results of the sighting will be filed on the report card.
sighted object: a large, silver object and two smaller, blinking objects
photographs: yes, the report indicates that the observer took photographs of the objects
